    <description>Process to update the date/time stamps on School Object from default of midnight UTC to add 12 hours for SF UI and Reporting Conversion.

05/28/25 - PE - Updated flow entry criteria to run whenever any of the fields mapped to have their date formatted is changed.
07/16/2025 - LK - Added logic to also update the Backdated Activation Dates
8/20/25 - JH - Updated formulas to set Backdated Activation Date = Stamp/Ingestion Date − 1 day so it reflects the actual trigger day (the prior day).
12.22.25 - LK - Added logic to look at the Funnel stage, to stamp the backdate when the stage = activated</description>
    <environments>Default</environments>
